title: 18. American Pandemic: When Is Enough, Enough?

description: What does America's future look like? In today's full length episode, we discuss the Coronavirus (COVID-19) Pandemic that's happening, how President Trump & Dr Fauci are handling the outbreak, and what we can learn from this crisis.
